title    : Chocolates
summary  : Kid in the Candy Store Templating
copyright: Copyright (c) 2010 Thomas Sawyer
license  : MIT
suite    : rubyworks
contact  : rubyworks-mailinglist@googlegroups.com

description:
  Chocolates is a meta-template engine. Like a box of choclates
  is allows you to pick and choose from a variety of rendering
  formats in the construction of a single document. Selection
  includes eruby, textile, markdown and many others.

authors:
- Thomas Sawyer

